    <li>questDescription(asker_royalInCurrentFaction==True)->[asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] [asker_nameFull] of [asker_faction_name] needs people to help [dutyRoyalDescription].\n\n[asker_pronoun] is asking you to lend [colonistCountToLend] to serve [asker_objective] for [lendForDays] days.\n\n[willSendShuttle]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount==1)->1 colonist[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount>1)->[colonistsToLendCount] colonists[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>willSendShuttle->[asker_pronoun] will send a shuttle to pick up the [colonists].</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount==1)->colonist</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount>1)->colonists</li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge==0)-></li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge>0)-> [minAge] years old or older</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount==1)->has</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount>1)->have</li>
  -->
  <PawnLend.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription(asker_factionLeader==True)->[asker_faction_leaderTitle] [asker_nameFull] من [asker_faction_name] يحتاج إلى أيادٍ إضافية للمساعدة في [dutyDescription].\n\n[asker_pronoun] يطلب منك إعارة [asker_objective] [colonistCountToLend] لمدة [lendForDays] أيام.\n\n[willSendShuttle]</li>
    <li>disease->إنفلونزا</li>
    <li>disease->طاعون</li>
    <li>disease->ملاريا</li>
    <li>disease->عدوى</li>
    <li>questDescription(asker_royalInCurrentFaction==True)->[asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] [asker_nameFull] من [asker_faction_name] يحتاج إلى أشخاص للمساعدة في [dutyRoyalDescription].\n\n[asker_pronoun] يطلب منك إعارة [colonistCountToLend] لخدمة [asker_objective] لمدة [lendForDays] أيام.\n\n[willSendShuttle]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount==1)->1 مستعمر[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount>1)->[colonistsToLendCount] مستعمرين[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>willSendShuttle->سيرسل [asker_pronoun] مكوكًا لاصطحاب [colonists].</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount==1)->مستعمر</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount>1)->مستعمرين</li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge==0)-></li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge>0)-> [minAge] سنة أو أكثر</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount==1)->has</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount>1)->have</li>
 </PawnLend.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
